name: FinderByGeoLocation
tagline: Now you can find shops, restaurants, ATMs, banks and gas stations near your location
body:
### Visit the Finder web application
If you are looking for ATMs, Shops, restaurants and many other needs near by your location or want to find in a specific location in the world.  Go ahead and [visit this page](https://github.com/rvrama/testrepo/blob/master/FindPlaceByGeoLoc.html)
